 STEAM PROTON v5.13 Launch Params
 
    PROTON_USE_D9VK=1 %command% RADV_PERFTEST=aco %command% PROTON_NO_ESYNC=1 %command% PROTON_NO_FSYNC=1 %command% gamemoderun %command%
 
 or just 
 
    PROTON_NO_ESYNC=1 %command%
    In Lutris set:
        Enable ACO Shader Compiler
        Enable Feral GameMode

 Then
    In game "Display Settings" enable "Monitor Vertical Sync"
    In game "Advanced Settings" enable "Framerate Stabilizer"
